<Speech gate:gateId="103156" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="102913" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="102306" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΟΥΣΑ</Parlmember> (<SpeechStart gate:gateId="102734" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="102468" majorType="speaker">Μαρία Κόλλια-Τσαρουχά</Chairman>):</SpeechStart></SpeechStart> Ωραία.
